title: WD My Passport Ultra 2TB USB 3.0 Portable Hard Drive $69.99
text:
WD My Passport Ultra 2TB USB 3.0 Portable Hard Drive $69.99 Posted 3 hours ago by Alex Chung 
Staples has the WD My Passport Ultra 2TB USB 3.0 Portable Hard Drive for a low $69.99 . Buy Online Pick Up In-Store. Tax in most states. 
This normally retails for $88, so you are saving $18 (20%) off with this deal. Over 270 reviews on Amazon with 4.5/5 star rating Secure portable storage with up to 2TB capacity Data transfer rates of up to 5 Gb/s Compatible with the USB 3.0 devices as well as many USB 2.0 devices Optional 256-bit AES hardware encryption Automatic local and cloud backup Formatted for Windows, reformatting required for Mac OSX
